\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4.2}{\ignorespaces AI orchestration loop. The model is called with the conversation history and the registered tool definitions. If the model emits a tool call, the orchestrator executes it, appends the result to the message history, and recalls the model. The loop terminates when the model produces a non-tool response, which is then streamed to the client.}}{29}{figure.caption.16}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:ai-loop}{{4.2}{29}{AI orchestration loop. The model is called with the conversation history and the registered tool definitions. If the model emits a tool call, the orchestrator executes it, appends the result to the message history, and recalls the model. The loop terminates when the model produces a non-tool response, which is then streamed to the client}{figure.caption.16}{}}
