\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4.3}{\ignorespaces The discussion view inside a project. Channels organize threaded conversations (project-wide and paper-scoped); the AI agent participates as a regular channel member but is implemented as the tool-orchestrated agent described in this section. The model picker at the top right routes between OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, and OpenRouter providers.}}{30}{figure.caption.17}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:ss-discussion-inline}{{4.3}{30}{The discussion view inside a project. Channels organize threaded conversations (project-wide and paper-scoped); the AI agent participates as a regular channel member but is implemented as the tool-orchestrated agent described in this section. The model picker at the top right routes between OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, and OpenRouter providers}{figure.caption.17}{}}
