\newlabel{sec:paper-discovery}{{4.6}{33}{Paper Discovery}{section.4.6}{}}
\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4.6}{\ignorespaces Paper discovery architecture. The query builder normalizes the user query for each source's expected syntax. The source router dispatches in parallel. As results arrive, the deduplicator collapses identical works using a union-find structure keyed by DOI, arXiv ID, and normalized title. The reranker applies semantic reranking when configured. Results are streamed as Server-Sent Events.}}{33}{figure.caption.21}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:discovery}{{4.6}{33}{Paper discovery architecture. The query builder normalizes the user query for each source's expected syntax. The source router dispatches in parallel. As results arrive, the deduplicator collapses identical works using a union-find structure keyed by DOI, arXiv ID, and normalized title. The reranker applies semantic reranking when configured. Results are streamed as Server-Sent Events}{figure.caption.21}{}}
