\newlabel{fig:ss-library-arch}{{4.7}{34}{The project library (References tab). Each entry shows title, authors, year, source, and a status indicator for AI ingestion (text extraction and embedding for retrieval). One-click actions are exposed for chat-with-paper, citation insertion into the active draft, and re-ingestion}{figure.caption.22}{}}
